// Trade Endpoints

### Get All Trades
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trades

### Get Trade by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trades/1

### Get Trade by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trades/99999

### Get Trade by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trades/invalid

### Get Trade by Listing
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings/1/trade

### Get Trade by Listing (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/listings/99999/trade

### Get Buyer's Trades
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/2/trades

### Get Buyer's Trades (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/trades

### Execute Trade
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "listingId": 1,
    "buyerId": 2
}

### Execute Trade (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "buyerId": 2
}

### Execute Trade (listing not found)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "listingId": 99999,
    "buyerId": 2
}

### Execute Trade (buy own listing)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trades
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "listingId": 1,
    "buyerId": 1
}

### Get Recent Trades (default limit)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trades/recent

### Get Recent Trades (limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trades/recent?limit=5

### Delete Trade
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/trades/1

### Delete Trade (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/trades/99999

### Count Total Trades
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trades/count

### Count Buyer's Trades
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/2/trades/count

### Count Buyer's Trades (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/trades/count
